title: Gambian Cup
text:
The Gambian Cup is the top knockout <a href="tournament">tournament</a> of the <a href="Gambia">Gambia</a>n <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a>. The current champion is <a href="Real%20Banjul">Real Banjul</a> who won their four title in 2019. The winner competes in the <a href="Gambian%20Super%20Cup">Gambian Super Cup</a> and also qualifies into the <a href="CAF%20Confederation%20Cup">CAF Confederation Cup</a> each season, if the national league champion also wins the FA cup then the second placed cup club competes.
<a href="Wallidan%20FC">Wallidan FC</a> has won the most titles, 23.
Performance by club.
Only cups after independence are counted.
